\par }\pard {\fs22 \tab The number of Tristaris is four; after the four elemental disasters that serve
 to remind that the world is headed for impending doom.  These are fire, flood, earthquake and storm.  Her symbol is one half of a face, with the narrowed eye shedding tears.
